Titolo: The Legend of Heroes II: Prophecy of the Moonlight Witch

Anno: 1994

Descrizione: The Legend of Heroes II: Prophecy of the Moonlight Witch, known in Japan as The Legend of Heroes III: Shiroki Majo, is a role-playing video game developed by Nihon Falcom. It is the third game in The Legend of Heroes series, and the first in the "Gagharv Trilogy", but was retitled to include a "two" in the title for its North American release. Originally released for the NEC PC-9801 in 1994, it was later re-released on several other platforms, including the Sega Saturn, PlayStation, and Microsoft Windows, before being released on the PlayStation Portable in 2006, the only version to be translated into English.